PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776636668
OL,3,CDowning Street rallies behind Starmer
OL,4,Cas he is expected to face 'judgment
OL,5,Cday'
OL,7,FSenior Government figures told the
OL,8,FGuardian newspaper that the Prime
OL,9,FMinister is facing "judgment day" next
OL,10,Fweek, when Sir Olly Robbins ` who was
OL,11,Fsacked this week as chief civil
OL,12,Fservant at the Foreign Office over the
OL,13,Flatest revelations about the scandal `
OL,14,Fis expected to appear before a
OL,15,Fcommittee of MPs.
OL,26,@qD@TOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
