OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776636668
OL,3,CDowning Street rallies behind Starmer
OL,4,Cas he is expected to face 'judgment
OL,5,Cday'
OL,7,FNo 10 on Friday night released a
OL,8,Freadout of a meeting between Sir Keir
OL,9,Fand senior civil servants that
OL,10,Fappeared to corroborate that the Prime
OL,11,FMinister only found out on Tuesday
OL,12,Fthat Lord Mandelson was cleared for
OL,13,Fhis role as Britain's representative
OL,14,Fin Washington against the advice of
OL,15,Fsecurity officials.
OL,17,FThe Foreign Office has been blamed for
OL,18,Fclearing the peer in January 2025 to
OL,19,Fbegin as US ambassador, despite him
OL,20,Ffailing a secure vetting process.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776636668
OL,3,CDowning Street rallies behind Starmer
OL,4,Cas he is expected to face 'judgment
OL,5,Cday'
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister has said he was
OL,8,F"absolutely furious", and described
OL,9,Fthe failure to inform him as
OL,10,F"staggering".
OL,12,FSir Olly, who was only weeks into his
OL,13,Fjob as Foreign Office permanent
OL,14,Fsecretary at the time, was sacked on
OL,15,FThursday as he had lost the confidence
OL,16,Fof Sir Keir and Foreign Secretary
OL,17,FYvette Cooper.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]rD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776636668
OL,3,CDowning Street rallies behind Starmer
OL,4,Cas he is expected to face 'judgment
OL,5,Cday'
OL,7,FHe is expected to speak to the Foreign
OL,8,FAffairs Committee as early as next
OL,9,FTuesday, a day after Sir Keir will
OL,10,Fupdate the House of Commons on the
OL,11,Flatest revelations about Lord
OL,12,FMandelson's appointment.
OL,14,FThe Guardian also reported on Friday
OL,15,Fthat Antonia Romeo, the head of the
OL,16,Fcivil service, and Cabinet Office
OL,17,Fpermanent secretary Catherine Little,
OL,18,Fhad found out before the Prime
OL,19,FMinister about Lord Mandelson's
OL,20,Ffailure to gain vetting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776636668
OL,3,CDowning Street rallies behind Starmer
OL,4,Cas he is expected to face 'judgment
OL,5,Cday'
OL,7,FThe readout of Tuesday's meeting gave
OL,8,Fcredence to this, as Ms Little had
OL,9,Freceived information about the vetting
OL,10,Fas part of the process to release
OL,11,Ffiles related to Lord Mandelson's
OL,12,Fappointment which MPs voted for in
OL,13,FFebruary.
OL,15,F"On reviewing the file she had
OL,16,Ftherefore learned that the
OL,17,Frecommendation from the vetting
OL,18,Fofficer had been that DV (Developed
OL,19,FVetting) should not be granted to
OL,20,FPeter Mandelson," the readout said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776636668
OL,3,CDowning Street rallies behind Starmer
OL,4,Cas he is expected to face 'judgment
OL,5,Cday'
OL,7,FThe Cabinet Office denied that this
OL,8,Fmeant the senior civil servant had sat
OL,9,Fon the details, while a Government
OL,10,Fsource said: "Cat has been the one
OL,11,Fdoggedly fighting Olly Robbins to get
OL,12,Fthe documents out of his clutches and
OL,13,Finto the public domain.
OL,15,F"This is a laughable attempt to shift
OL,16,Fblame from the actual person who kept
OL,17,Fthe PM in the dark."
OL,26,@rD@NOUwD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
