CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776636668
OL,3,CDowning Street rallies behind Starmer
OL,4,Cas he is expected to face 'judgment
OL,5,Cday'
OL,7,FThe leaders of the major opposition
OL,8,Fparties have all called for Sir Keir
OL,9,Fto resign over the latest revelations,
OL,10,Fwith Kemi Badenoch claiming the Prime
OL,11,FMinister had misled Parliament and the
OL,12,Fpublic.
OL,14,FLord Mandelson, a political
OL,15,Fappointment rather than a career
OL,16,Fdiplomat, was sacked from his
OL,17,FWashington role last September when
OL,18,Fmore details emerged about his
OL,19,Frelationship with paedophile financier
OL,20,FJeffrey Epstein, who died in 2019.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
