PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776636668
OL,3,CDowning Street rallies behind Starmer
OL,4,Cas he is expected to face 'judgment
OL,5,Cday'
OL,7,FSir Keir was already under fire over
OL,8,Fthe decision to give Lord Mandelson
OL,9,Fthe job, despite it being known that
OL,10,Fhis dealings with Epstein continued
OL,11,Fafter the financier's conviction for
OL,12,Fchild sex offences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
